1. CTRL+SHIFT+P => Docker: Add Dockerfiles to workspace

2. Terminal: (<commit hash> =) git describe --always --dirty

3. CTRL+SHIFT+P => Docker: Build Image => pvandorp/docker-express:<commit hash>

4. CTRL+SHIFT+P => Docker: Run => pvandorp/docker-express:<commit hash>

5. Browse to http://localhost:3000

6. Terminal => docker ps => copy <container id>

7. Terminal => docker rm -f <container id>

8. CTRL+SHIFT+P => Docker: Push => pvandorp/docker-express:<commit hash>

9. Show docker hub